There isn&#39;t any integer type for cells, we just have float. To convert the floating number to an integer just use int as:

    for i in range(sheet.nrows):
        print (int(sheet.cell_value(i,0)))

and subsequently for the string as :

    for i in range(sheet.nrows):
        print (str(sheet.cell_value(i,0)))

