I&#39;m making a java to python translator with the help of the flex and bison tools. The bison rules refer to a restriction of java grammar. In addition to creating the rules in bison, I also created the Abstract Syntax Tree as an Intermediate Representation. The respective nodes of the AST were created in the semantic actions alongside the bison rules.

